Package eu.cqse.check.framework.statements

Parsers that look inside an entity to determine specific properties of that entity, e.g. which variables are declared there.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IVariableDefinitionParser
    Given a shallow entity, returns all variables/parameters/fields that are defined in that entity.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CLikeVariableDefinitionParserBase
    Base class for variable definition parsers of C-like languages.
    CsVariableDefinitionParser
    Parses variable/field/parameter definitions in C#.
    JavaVariableDefinitionParser
    Parses variable/field/parameter definitions in Java.
    StatementParserFactory
    Factory that can create parsers that look inside a shallow entity.
    VariableDefinition
    Represents a variable/field/parameter definition.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    VariableDefinition.EVariableType
    The type of a variable definition.
